      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan020.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。莉央か沙季に「こころが落とし物してたから\n代わりに渡しておいて」とか言ってみるのはどう？",
      "startTime": 248.2742701373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
